title: PPPP’s  Mahmood Alam Jamot wins PS- 87 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP),Mahmood Alam Jamot has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-87, Malir-4 , by securing 19,220 votes.
According to unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate Taus Khan, who bagged vote 7,703.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 44.79 %.
